    <item>
      <title>【笔记】MacOS计划任务</title>
      <link>https://feiju12138.github.io/2020/10/04/MacOS%E8%AE%A1%E5%88%92%E4%BB%BB%E5%8A%A1/</link>
      <guid>https://feiju12138.github.io/2020/10/04/MacOS%E8%AE%A1%E5%88%92%E4%BB%BB%E5%8A%A1/</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 04 Oct 2020 05:39:54 GMT</pubDate>
      <description>
      
        &lt;h2 id=&quot;前言&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#前言&quot; class=&quot;headerlink&quot; title=&quot;前言&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;前言&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;MacOS除了可以使用Linux的crontab方式执行计划任务，还可以使用launchctl执行计划任务&lt;/p&gt;
      
      </description>
      
      
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<link rel="stylesheet" class="aplayer-secondary-style-marker" href="/assets/css/APlayer.min.css"><script src="/assets/js/APlayer.min.js" class="aplayer-secondary-script-marker"></script><h2 id="前言"><a href="#前言" class="headerlink" title="前言"></a>前言</h2><p>MacOS除了可以使用Linux的crontab方式执行计划任务，还可以使用launchctl执行计划任务</p><a id="more"></a><h2 id="计划任务"><a href="#计划任务" class="headerlink" title="计划任务"></a>计划任务</h2><h3 id="创建执行的脚本"><a href="#创建执行的脚本" class="headerlink" title="创建执行的脚本"></a>创建执行的脚本</h3><ul><li>创建一个脚本文件</li></ul><figure class="highlight sh"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">touch run.sh</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>编辑脚本</li></ul><figure class="highlight sh"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">vim run.sh</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>将脚本权限改为可执行权限</li></ul><figure class="highlight sh"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">chmod 777 run.sh</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="创建计划任务脚本"><a href="#创建计划任务脚本" class="headerlink" title="创建计划任务脚本"></a>创建计划任务脚本</h3><ul><li>在<code>~/Library/LaunchAgents</code>目录下创建<code>com.demo.plist</code>文件</li></ul><blockquote><p>其他目录</p><blockquote><p><code>~/Library/LaunchAgents</code>：由用户自己定义的任务项<br><code>/Library/LaunchAgents</code>：由管理员为用户定义的任务项<br><code>/Library/LaunchDaemons</code>：由管理员定义的守护进程任务项<br><code>/System/Library/LaunchAgents</code>：由Mac OS X为用户定义的任务项<br><code>/System/Library/LaunchDaemons</code>：由Mac OS X定义的守护进程任务项</p></blockquote></blockquote><figure class="highlight sh"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">cd</span> ~/Library/LaunchAgents</span><br><span class="line">touch com.demo.plist</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>编辑配置文件</li></ul><blockquote><p><code>Label</code>：对应的需要保证全局唯一性<br><code>Program</code>：要运行的程序位置<br><code>ProgramArguments</code>：命令语句</p></blockquote><blockquote><p><code>StartInterval</code>：时间间隔，指定脚本每间隔多长时间（单位：秒）<br>执行一次<br><code>StartCalendarInterval</code>：运行的时间（StartInterval与StartCalendarInterval只能出现一个）</p><blockquote><p><code>dict</code>：单个时间点<br><code>array</code>：多个时间点</p><blockquote><p><code>Minute</code>：定义分钟<br><code>Hour</code>：定义小时<br><code>Day</code>：定义天<br><code>Weekday</code>：定义星期（0和7都表示星期日）<br><code>Month</code>：定义月份</p></blockquote></blockquote></blockquote><blockquote><p><code>StandardOutPath</code>：日志输出位置<br><code>StandardErrorPath</code>：报错日志输出位置</p></blockquote><figure class="highlight xml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">&lt;?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&lt;!DOCTYPE plist PUBLIC "-//Apple//DTD PLIST 1.0//EN" "http://www.apple.com/DTDs/PropertyList-1.0.dtd"&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">plist</span> <span class="attr">version</span>=<span class="string">"1.0"</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">dict</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">key</span>&gt;</span>Label<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">key</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">string</span>&gt;</span>com.demo.plist<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">string</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">key</span>&gt;</span>ProgramArguments<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">key</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">array</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">string</span>&gt;</span>~/run.sh<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">string</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">array</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">key</span>&gt;</span>StartCalendarInterval<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">key</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">dict</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">key</span>&gt;</span>Minute<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">key</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">integer</span>&gt;</span>00<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">integer</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">key</span>&gt;</span>Hour<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">key</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">integer</span>&gt;</span>08<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">integer</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">dict</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">key</span>&gt;</span>StandardOutPath<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">key</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">string</span>&gt;</span>~/run.log<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">string</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">key</span>&gt;</span>StandardErrorPath<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">key</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">string</span>&gt;</span>~/run.err<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">string</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">dict</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">plist</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="计划任务的操作"><a href="#计划任务的操作" class="headerlink" title="计划任务的操作"></a>计划任务的操作</h3><h4 id="加载计划任务"><a href="#加载计划任务" class="headerlink" title="加载计划任务"></a>加载计划任务</h4><ul><li>start和unload之前必须先加载计划任务</li></ul><blockquote><p><code>&lt;plist&gt;</code>：<code>.plist</code>结尾的计划任务配置文件</p></blockquote><figure class="highlight sh"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">launchctl load &lt;plist&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h5 id="将plist文件中无效的key覆盖掉"><a href="#将plist文件中无效的key覆盖掉" class="headerlink" title="将plist文件中无效的key覆盖掉"></a>将plist文件中无效的key覆盖掉</h5><figure class="highlight sh"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">launchctl load -w &lt;plist&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="删除计划任务"><a href="#删除计划任务" class="headerlink" title="删除计划任务"></a>删除计划任务</h4><ul><li>如果任务修改了，那么必须先unload，然后重新load</li></ul><figure class="highlight sh"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">launchctl unload &lt;plist&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="查看所有计划任务"><a href="#查看所有计划任务" class="headerlink" title="查看所有计划任务"></a>查看所有计划任务</h4><figure class="highlight sh"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">launchctl list</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h5 id="查看指定计划任务"><a href="#查看指定计划任务" class="headerlink" title="查看指定计划任务"></a>查看指定计划任务</h5><figure class="highlight sh"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">launchctl list | grep <span class="string">"&lt;plist&gt;"</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="开始计划任务"><a href="#开始计划任务" class="headerlink" title="开始计划任务"></a>开始计划任务</h4><ul><li>立即测试计划任务，不论时间到没到</li></ul><figure class="highlight sh"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">launchctl start &lt;plist&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="结束计划任务"><a href="#结束计划任务" class="headerlink" title="结束计划任务"></a>结束计划任务</h4><figure class="highlight sh"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">launchctl stop &lt;plist&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="完成"><a href="#完成" class="headerlink" title="完成"></a>完成</h2><h2 id="参考文献"><a href="#参考文献" class="headerlink" title="参考文献"></a>参考文献</h2><p><a href="https://www.jianshu.com/p/4addd9b455f2" target="_blank" rel="noopener">间书——繁著</a></p>]]></content:encoded>
      
